    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075600/extras/3c9939e4174977eedcd176bd510c2284.poster.avif?t=1755274192\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075600/extras/3c9939e4174977eedcd176bd510c2284.webm?t=1755274192\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075600/extras/3c9939e4174977eedcd176bd510c2284.mp4?t=1755274192\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Atrion Project》是一款节奏紧凑、充满张力的2D动作游戏，融合了砍杀、平台跳跃以及“死亡重试”的玩法，设定在一个黑暗而神秘的科幻世界中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你将扮演 Atrion —— 一个失去记忆的赛博混合体，流落在未知星球上。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的任务：找回飞船的零件，击败致命的敌人，揭开你真实身份的秘密……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这场旅途中，你并不孤单，还有一些关键盟友会协助你。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075600/extras/7361fc46c9be60bae7a22beed524f89a.poster.avif?t=1755274192\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075600/extras/7361fc46c9be60bae7a22beed524f89a.webm?t=1755274192\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075600/extras/7361fc46c9be60bae7a22beed524f89a.mp4?t=1755274192\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >操控一个流畅直观的战斗系统，响应迅速、节奏明快 —— 没有复杂操作，只有精准与打击感。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >解锁独特技能，在不断进阶的挑战中击败令人难忘的Boss战斗，考验你的反应和节奏掌握。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075600/extras/f292ba763103a8852c0a742c91afbab7.poster.avif?t=1755274192\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075600/extras/f292ba763103a8852c0a742c91afbab7.webm?t=1755274192\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075600/extras/f292ba763103a8852c0a742c91afbab7.mp4?t=1755274192\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >强化 Atrion，解锁多样能力，根据你的战斗风格自由调整，克服不断升级的挑战。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075600/extras/db10bf97253a6c96e2b5b0b00ac00594.poster.avif?t=1755274192\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075600/extras/db10bf97253a6c96e2b5b0b00ac00594.webm?t=1755274192\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075600/extras/db10bf97253a6c96e2b5b0b00ac00594.mp4?t=1755274192\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >挑战是严峻的 —— 但始终公平。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每一次胜利，都会让你更接近真相。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075600/extras/a6f9328a92b071e7075b2923f59610dd.poster.avif?t=1755274192\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075600/extras/a6f9328a92b071e7075b2923f59610dd.webm?t=1755274192\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075600/extras/a6f9328a92b071e7075b2923f59610dd.mp4?t=1755274192\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>推荐给喜爱以下作品的玩家：</strong> <br><i>《Dead Cells》, 《ScourgeBringer》, 《Katana Zero》, 《Axiom Verge》, 《Furi》</i> <br><i>以及喜爱风格化、神秘且充满敌意的科幻世界的玩家。</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>你会倒下。学习。再来。</strong> <br><strong>最好现在就准备好。</strong> <br><strong>立即将本作添加至愿望单。</strong></p>",
